<p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;">会议首先对发展对象进行深入了解，程杨胜校长和经济管理学院组织专员、学生支部书记陈莹，严格把关发展对象质量，根据其实际情况进行深入剖析，并对学生们寄予众望，提出相应的建议，鼓励他们保持高昂的学习状态，紧紧跟党走。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEIMYonUoCYTV6M1sDHTMtkDPf8244rz5LfwtJkInO8P49V1j5VoCPbxGqyO5uNbVjhvnVicjNkbFkw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="309" height="213" style="width: 309px; height: 213px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">谈心谈话后，程杨胜校长带领全体发展对象</span><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-indent: 2em; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">提出四点要求：</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">一、认真学习贯彻二十大精神，推动党的二十大精神走深走实，用新的伟大奋斗创造新的伟业。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">二、加强对自己约束，坚守纪律规则，时刻牢记党的纪律，严格要求自身。持续加强学习，筑牢思想防线。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">三、发挥先锋模范作用，处处以身作则，在各项工作和活动中走在群众的前面，成为群众学习的榜样。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: inherit; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">四、学习新党章，奋进新征程。自觉履行职务，始终保持旺盛的革命斗志和与时俱进的精神状态。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><br/></p>